eu.advance.logistics.flow.engine
Class AdvanceDefaultSchemaResolver

java.lang.Object
  eu.advance.logistics.flow.engine.AdvanceDefaultSchemaResolver
All Implemented Interfaces:
AdvanceSchemaResolver
public class AdvanceDefaultSchemaResolver
extends java.lang.Object
implements AdvanceSchemaResolver

Class to resolve schemas and load them as XTypes from local file system. If the schemas starting with advance cannot be resolved as a local file, the code attempts to resolve it against the classpath root.

Author:
akarnokd, 2011.09.28.
